# Upstream files not applicable to this port BY DESIGN, with the reason.
# Format: <upstream path> <TAB> <reason>. Anything else uncovered is either
# unported surface or ported code missing its upstream citation -- both are debt
# the map report exists to show, so keep this list to true design decisions.
src/tune.cpp	SPSA tuning framework: not ported by design; tuned values are transcribed constants
src/tune.h	companion of tune.cpp
src/incbin/incbin.h	net embedding machinery: zfish loads the net at runtime by design (NNUE_EMBEDDING_OFF)
src/thread_win32_osx.h	upstream's win/osx threading shim: zfish owns its thread runtime in src/platform/
src/universal/entry_x86.cpp	fat-binary entry shim: zfish builds one binary per arch
src/universal/entry_arm64.cpp	fat-binary entry shim: zfish builds one binary per arch
src/universal/entry_riscv64.cpp	fat-binary entry shim: zfish builds one binary per arch
src/universal/nnue_embed.cpp	net embedding machinery: zfish loads the net at runtime by design
